---
title: Playgrounds
permalink: /playgrounds/
description: "Playgrounds are things I explore freely: emergent, open-ended, curiosity-driven play."
---
<div class="max-w-5xl">
    <div class="border border-dashed border-stone-300 p-4 bg-stone-100 mb-12">
        <header class="mb-4">
            <h1 class="uppercase tracking-wider font-jersey text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-normal mb-1">Playgrounds <span
                        class="lowercase text-emerald-600/80">/ <span id="typewriter"
                                                                      class="after:content-['\_'] after:animate-blink italic font-normal"></span></span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm italic">Things I explore freely.</p>
        </header>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-px justify-stretch bg-stone-50">
            <div class="ring ring-stone-200 p-4 grow">
                <p class="text-xs font-light uppercase mb-1">Shape</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Emergent, open-ended.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ring ring-stone-200 p-4 grow">
                <p class="text-xs font-light uppercase mb-1">Logic</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Curiosity-driven improvisation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ring ring-stone-200 p-4 grow">
                <p class="text-xs font-light uppercase mb-1">Structure</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Loosely connected or associative.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ring ring-stone-200 p-4 grow">
                <p class="text-xs font-light uppercase mb-1">Action</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Wandering and playing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ring ring-stone-200 p-4 grow">
                <p class="text-xs font-light uppercase mb-1">Mode</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Lateral, intuitive, divergent.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ring ring-stone-200 p-4 grow">
                <p class="text-xs font-light uppercase mb-1">Data</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Fragments, relations, sources.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ring ring-stone-200 p-4 grow">
                <p class="text-xs font-light uppercase mb-1">Relation</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Feeds practices and projects; receives overflow.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="max-w-4xl">
    <ol>
        {%- for post in collections.playgroundSorted -%}
            <li>
                <span class="flex group relative">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                         class="size-4 shrink-0 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:text-emerald-600 cursor-help absolute top-1.5"
                         fill="currentColor"
                         viewBox="0 0 16 16" data-tooltip="Playground">
                        <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14m0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16"/>
                        <path d="M8 1 L14.062 11.5 L1.938 11.5 Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                              stroke-width="1"/>
                    </svg>
                    <a class="pl-6.5" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </span>
            </li>
        {%- endfor -%}
    </ol>
</div>